longBusinessSummary: Dustin Group AB (publ) provides online IT products and services in Nordic and Benelux regions. It operates through two segments, Small and Medium-Sized Businesses, and Large Corporate and Public Sector. The company offers hardware, software, and related services and solutions. It acts as a strategic IT partner for small and medium-sized businesses, large sized businesses, and public sector and consumers. The company was founded in 1984 and is headquartered in Nacka Strand, Sweden. Dustin Group AB (publ) is a subsidiary of AxMedia AB.
